  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kong Fu is a boxing game where the raw power of wild gorillas meets unpredictable ragdoll physics. Dive into fast-paced, over-the-top brawls as gorillas throw punches, launch into acrobatic stunts by accident, and tumble through the ring in a hilarious display of force and chaos. Gone are the days of practicing combos for hours, as in Kong Fu, you never see the same move occur twice.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kong Fu is a boxing game where the raw power of wild gorillas meets unpredictable ragdoll physics. Dive into fast-paced, over-the-top brawls as gorillas throw punches, launch into acrobatic stunts by accident, and tumble through the ring in a hilarious display of force and chaos. Gone are the days of practicing combos for hours, as in Kong Fu, you never see the same move occur twice.</p>",
